  0 _< f1 _< 3 Sign of positive mantissae
  0 _< n _< 1  Zero before .
  0 _< bE _< 7 No. of digits in exponent
  0 _< f2 _< 3 Sign of exponent
  0 _< g _< 15 Grouping of decimals
